The paper discusses the neural realization of the SP theory, which is related to neural networks and artificial intelligence (cs.NE, cs.AI). It also discusses unsupervised learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a new concept of cell assemblies, which is related to the organization of neural networks (cs.CC). Finally, the paper discusses how these structures can be used to form hierarchies and other knowledge structures, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY).
